c: 16
v: 106
t: "“Amene akukana Allah, pambuyo pomukhulupirira, (chilango chachikulu chikumuyembekezera), kupatula yemwe adakakamizidwa, uku mtima wake utakhazikika pa chikhulupiliro; koma amene akutsekulira mtima wake kusakhulupirira, mkwiyo wa Allah uli pa iwo (ndipo anthu otere) adzapata chilango chachikulu"